<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,1921,2018]" lastBlockId="17.[151,1437,151,429]" lastPageId="17" lastPageNumber="418" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">
<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="417" type="discussion">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,316,1921,1946]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">Variation.</emphasis>
Head longer; sensilla aligned in longitudinal series of 
<quantity box="[946,991,1921,1946]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.032" pageId="16" pageNumber="417" unit="in" value="8.0">8 in</quantity>
each flagellomere; vertex less convex; metapostnotal median carina complete or failed posteriorly; spots of metasomal tergite II elliptical.
</subSubSection>
